@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.90) + (v1 + 0.81 / tmp + 0.59)))
    v0 = 0.17
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.77)))
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.87 / v0 + 0.84) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.21)) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.45) * v2))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.60)) - (wp.abs(v2 + 0.61) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.73)))
    data[tid] = v0
